{"type":"message","id":"10c9043b","parentId":"5e6fc992","timestamp":"2026-05-31T17:59:41.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know the registered cron jobs. Let me summarize them clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"就两个，凌晨三点多刚跑完：\n\n**1. faye-dreaming**\n- 每天凌晨 3:00（上海时区）跑\n- 干的事：遍历用户更新记忆、写encountings、调心境指标、写梦、生成pending_urges\n- 上次跑了2分14秒，状态ok\n\n**2. faye-pending-urges**\n- 每6小时跑一次（带5分钟随机偏移）\n- 检查 pending_urges.md 有没有攒着没说的话→条件满足就推给你\n- 上次跑了43秒，状态ok\n\n就这两个，没别的了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2220,"output":154,"cacheRead":20608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":16,"totalTokens":22982,"cost":{"input":0.0003108,"output":0.00004312,"cacheRead":0.000577024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000930944}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780250378466,"responseId":"acc1e224-47ac-457e-8e8e-6322a48f6e48"}}
