{"type":"message","id":"c84ff763","parentId":"1d8676bb","timestamp":"2026-05-31T18:48:35.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So 汀桑 actually composed 6 songs today. Interesting mix - first a funny \"求群友救济\" (begging for help from friends) in two versions (15s meme version and 141s sad erhu version), then a whole series about \"猫耳小萝莉\" (cat-ear little girl) - 4 iterations.\n\nThe 0004 has group_id = cron, which means it was auto-triggered by a cron job. And 0006 has group_id = group_compose.\n\nLet me relay this to 汀桑 in Faye style.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Son 翻出来了👊\n\n你今天整了 **6 首**，够狠的。\n\n**第一波 00:12~00:20 —「求群友救济」**\n- 先搞了个 15s 网络整活版\n- 又来了个凄惨二胡民乐版，2 分 21 秒\n- 歌词是\"六月份到现在一顿饭都没吃\"——你这歌词是写实还是整活😏\n\n**第二波 01:38~01:52 —「猫耳小萝莉」四连发**\n- 从「猫耳小萝莉的陪伴」到「守夜童谣」，同一套设定跑了 4 次\n- 诡异又可爱 + 电子童谣，一条路走到黑\n- 第 0004 号是 cron 自动触发的，第 0006 号标了 group_compose\n- 后面两条没歌词——纯音乐迭代？\n\n6 个 mp3 都在，文件都健在。reset 了归 reset，活是一个没少干啊🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":402,"output":352,"cacheRead":36608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":120,"totalTokens":37362,"cost":{"input":0.00005628,"output":0.00009856,"cacheRead":0.001025024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001179864}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780253311536,"responseId":"431fdbd8-c93f-48dc-8abd-e5614975e13a"}}
